title: Couple With Heart Person Person Medium Dark Skin Tone Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a ropersontic couple with a heart between them, specifically showing a person with a medium-dark skin tone and a person with a dark skin tone. It signifies love, partnership, and affection between two individuals.
apple_vendor_description: This touching emoji on Apple devices illustrates a couple with both individuals rendered in darker skin tones, one medium-dark and the other dark, sharing a loving embrace. The signature glossy 3D shading and realistic lighting on Apple devices highlight the warmth and connection between them, with a prominent, glowing heart at their center. It's a powerful and inclusive depiction of love and unity, ideal for expressing deep affection and partnership.
